Class GarageTableView

  • java.lang.Object
    • view.GarageTableView

  • public class GarageTableView
extends java.lang.Object
    GarageTableView is not a table view. It is a GridPane inside a ScrollPane. It requires a ParkingLot object to be constructed. The public function refreshGrid requires a ParkingLot object, and refreshes the grid Has a getter and setter for the ScrollPane
    Author:
    chris
